data.description: This well maintained 4 Bedroom home has an den an open floor plan and with a little over 2000 square feet of living area there is plenty of space to entertain family and friends. You will love the master suite with 2 walk-in closets, dual vanities, and a large walk-in shower with dual showerheads. This home features tile flooring throughout, a large kitchen Island, Breakfast Bar, Pantry and Stainless Steel Appliances. The great room flows right in to the lanai where you can enjoy gatherings indoor and outdoor. This home has a privacy fence and large backyard and plenty of room for a pool. This home is NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE- NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED. Make your appointment to see this home before its gone!
